01:09:40,979 --> 01:09:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] korizma i došašće.

645
01:09:42,880 --> 01:09:45,140
[SPEAKER_00] Plus još tri ciklusa u godinu

646
01:09:45,140 --> 01:09:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] uoči duhova

647
01:09:46,699 --> 01:09:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] 9 dana najčešće.

648
01:09:48,199 --> 01:09:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim jedne ljetne

649
01:09:49,619 --> 01:09:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne vježbe

650
01:09:50,539 --> 01:09:52,520
[SPEAKER_00] od 7 do 9 dana.

651
01:09:52,520 --> 01:09:54,479
[SPEAKER_00] I budući da smo mi

652
01:09:54,479 --> 01:09:55,399
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevci,

653
01:09:55,399 --> 01:09:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] evo uoči

654
01:09:56,659 --> 01:09:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] Svetkovine Svetog Franje

655
01:09:58,420 --> 01:09:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] to je konac Rui

656
01:09:59,300 --> 01:10:00,779
[SPEAKER_00] na početak desetog mjeseca.

657
01:10:00,779 --> 01:10:01,819
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to je nešto

658
01:10:01,819 --> 01:10:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] najvažnije.

659
01:10:02,579 --> 01:10:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

660
01:10:02,880 --> 01:10:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] sve ove prethodne

661
01:10:04,199 --> 01:10:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] duhovne vježbe

662
01:10:05,000 --> 01:10:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] koje su objavljene

663
01:10:06,159 --> 01:10:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi će pronaći tamo.

664
01:10:08,119 --> 01:10:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] To će biti jedna šuma

665
01:10:09,000 --> 01:10:09,399
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj,

666
01:10:09,399 --> 01:10:10,600
[SPEAKER_00] ti nekih duhovnih vježbi.

667
01:10:10,600 --> 01:10:11,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ako sad netko

668
01:10:11,760 --> 01:10:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] recimo instalira aplikaciju

669
01:10:13,260 --> 01:10:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] zna će vidjeti

670
01:10:13,739 --> 01:10:14,300
[SPEAKER_00] u ponudi

671
01:10:14,300 --> 01:10:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] puno dostupnih

672
01:10:15,800 --> 01:10:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] dostupnih vježbi.

673
01:10:16,760 --> 01:10:17,399
[SPEAKER_00] Osim toga,

674
01:10:17,399 --> 01:10:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono što je postalo simpatično

675
01:10:19,460 --> 01:10:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] i ljudi mi se često jave

676
01:10:21,680 --> 01:10:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvale

677
01:10:22,899 --> 01:10:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] to je

678
01:10:23,340 --> 01:10:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] F-a riječi.

679
01:10:24,859 --> 01:10:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] F-a kao jedna mjera

680
01:10:26,939 --> 01:10:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] ima u opisu tamo

681
01:10:29,659 --> 01:10:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] jedna mala ikonica

682
01:10:31,199 --> 01:10:32,399
[SPEAKER_00] iznad gore u desnom kutu

683
01:10:32,399 --> 01:10:33,460
[SPEAKER_00] tu je opis što znači

684
01:10:33,460 --> 01:10:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] F-a riječi.

685
01:10:34,300 --> 01:10:34,979
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo,

686
01:10:34,979 --> 01:10:35,479
[SPEAKER_00] to je ono

687
01:10:35,479 --> 01:10:36,979
[SPEAKER_00] 20 kila riječi,

688
01:10:36,979 --> 01:10:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] jedna mjera za težinu

689
01:10:38,140 --> 01:10:39,399
[SPEAKER_00] u starom zavijetu.

690
01:10:39,659 --> 01:10:41,439
[SPEAKER_00] jedan komad riječi

691
01:10:41,439 --> 01:10:43,939
[SPEAKER_00] Božije iz dnevnog evanđelja

692
01:10:43,939 --> 01:10:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji je kratko protumačen.

693
01:10:45,539 --> 01:10:46,439
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, nekako

694
01:10:46,439 --> 01:10:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] barem toliko

695
01:10:47,720 --> 01:10:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] te riječi Božije

696
01:10:50,220 --> 01:10:51,619
[SPEAKER_00] primiti u sebe

697
01:10:51,619 --> 01:10:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] u tom danu

698
01:10:52,760 --> 01:10:54,720
[SPEAKER_00] i kratko je razmatrati

699
01:10:54,720 --> 01:10:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] da bi Božja riječ

700
01:10:55,960 --> 01:10:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] u nama donosila svoje plodove.

701
01:10:58,119 --> 01:11:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] Osim toga,

702
01:11:00,079 --> 01:11:01,420
[SPEAKER_00] tu su dnevna čitanja,

703
01:11:01,420 --> 01:11:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] misna čitanja

704
01:11:03,260 --> 01:11:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] i to je jedno veliko pomagalo.

705
01:11:05,140 --> 01:11:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ta čitanja preuzimamo sa HILPA,

706
01:11:08,500 --> 01:11:10,560
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski institut za liturgijski pastoral,

707
01:11:10,560 --> 01:11:12,079
[SPEAKER_00] to je njihovom dobrotom

708
01:11:12,079 --> 01:11:13,359
[SPEAKER_00] i njihovom suglasnošću

709
01:11:13,359 --> 01:11:15,439
[SPEAKER_00] i to je, ja bih rekao,

710
01:11:15,439 --> 01:11:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] puno važnije od duhovnih vježbi.

711
01:11:17,500 --> 01:11:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, već smo mi to govorili.

712
01:11:19,119 --> 01:11:20,439
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je važno

713
01:11:20,439 --> 01:11:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] hraniti se riječi Božijom.

714
01:11:22,039 --> 01:11:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je to važno.

715
01:11:23,340 --> 01:11:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] To je presudno

716
01:11:24,220 --> 01:11:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] za naš duhovni život.

717
01:11:25,380 --> 01:11:26,720
[SPEAKER_00] I, evo,

718
01:11:26,720 --> 01:11:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] aplikacija e-duhovne vježbe

719
01:11:28,960 --> 01:11:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] koja se može, dakle,

720
01:11:29,779 --> 01:11:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] bestplatno preuzeti,

721
01:11:30,880 --> 01:11:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] ona nudi

722
01:11:32,960 --> 01:11:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] za svaki dan ta misna čitanja.

723
01:11:35,920 --> 01:11:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] I tu su još neka svjedočanstva,

724
01:11:37,779 --> 01:11:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] novosti i tako dalje.

725
01:11:39,239 --> 01:11:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] Valjda sam sve rekao.

726
01:11:40,220 --> 01:11:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] Upravo ta EFA riječ

727
01:11:42,039 --> 01:11:43,359
[SPEAKER_01] bi mogla biti

728
01:11:43,359 --> 01:11:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] dobar početak za jutro,

729
01:11:44,880 --> 01:11:46,119
[SPEAKER_01] što ste već spominjali

730
01:11:46,119 --> 01:11:47,060
[SPEAKER_01] u vezi molitve,

731
01:11:47,060 --> 01:11:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] kratak,

732
01:11:47,760 --> 01:11:49,680
[SPEAKER_01] pročitat dnevno evanđer,

733
01:11:49,680 --> 01:11:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] još imamo kratak komentar.

734
01:11:51,600 --> 01:11:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa imamo dosta svjedočanstva,

735
01:11:53,920 --> 01:11:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne objavimo to,

736
01:11:54,920 --> 01:11:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] nismo baš toliko ni ažurni.

737
01:11:56,460 --> 01:11:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] Stvarno imamo dobrih svjedočanstava,

738
01:11:59,260 --> 01:12:01,260
[SPEAKER_00] ili o, ajmo tako reći,

739
01:12:01,260 --> 01:12:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] suživotu s našom aplikacijom,

740
01:12:03,119 --> 01:12:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] evo, baš ono,

741
01:12:04,979 --> 01:12:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] osobe jutro

742
01:12:06,760 --> 01:12:08,939
[SPEAKER_00] provedu sa našom aplikacijom,

743
01:12:08,939 --> 01:12:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] evo, baš hraneći se Božijom riječju

744
01:12:11,039 --> 01:12:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] i slušajući

745
01:12:12,859 --> 01:12:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] EF-u riječi

746
01:12:14,340 --> 01:12:15,579
[SPEAKER_00] i razmatrajući,

747
01:12:15,579 --> 01:12:15,979
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, evo,

748
01:12:15,979 --> 01:12:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što su poslušali EF-u riječi,

749
01:12:18,039 --> 01:12:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] često znaju ostati

750
01:12:19,380 --> 01:12:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] u jednom svom osobnom razmatranju,

751
01:12:21,420 --> 01:12:22,840
[SPEAKER_00] u šutnji osobnom razmatranju,

752
01:12:22,840 --> 01:12:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] osobnom predanju.

753
01:12:23,880 --> 01:12:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, imate, suradnike.

754
01:12:26,260 --> 01:12:27,380
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, imamo,

755
01:12:27,380 --> 01:12:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo baš blagoslovljeni,

756
01:12:29,000 --> 01:12:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo baš blagoslovljeni suradnicima

757
01:12:31,119 --> 01:12:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] i sve je to na volonterskoj bazi,

758
01:12:34,079 --> 01:12:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, evo, tu su,

759
01:12:35,739 --> 01:12:37,920
[SPEAKER_00] kao nekakvi voditelji,

760
01:12:37,920 --> 01:12:38,619
[SPEAKER_00] to smo nas,

761
01:12:38,619 --> 01:12:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] trojica fratara iz Pazina,

762
01:12:40,579 --> 01:12:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] osim mene tu je fradarko Tepert,

763
01:12:43,640 --> 01:12:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] spomenuti već,

764
01:12:44,579 --> 01:12:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] koji se nalazi na službi

765
01:12:45,800 --> 01:12:46,699
[SPEAKER_00] trenutno u Rimu.

766
01:12:46,699 --> 01:12:49,520
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je naš fra Marinko Klajić,

767
01:12:49,520 --> 01:12:50,600
[SPEAKER_00] koji više nije fra,

768
01:12:50,600 --> 01:12:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] on je napredovao

769
01:12:52,319 --> 01:12:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] u svom duhovnom životu,

770
01:12:53,619 --> 01:12:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa je on sad pustinjak,

771
01:12:55,699 --> 01:12:57,680
[SPEAKER_00] biskupijski pustinjak

772
01:12:57,680 --> 01:13:01,060
[SPEAKER_00] u Gospičko-senjskoj biskupiji

773
01:13:01,060 --> 01:13:02,680
[SPEAKER_00] i on je sad brat,

774
01:13:02,680 --> 01:13:03,739
[SPEAKER_00] Marinko Klajić.

775
01:13:03,739 --> 01:13:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, nas trojica konstantno radimo

776
01:13:06,460 --> 01:13:09,680
[SPEAKER_00] na održavanju aplikacije,

777
01:13:09,680 --> 01:13:12,439
[SPEAKER_00] na redovitom administriranju.

778
01:13:13,039 --> 01:13:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je sad evo jako važan Vlado,

779
01:13:15,199 --> 01:13:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] Vlado Rosančić,

780
01:13:16,319 --> 01:13:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] koji je programer,

781
01:13:17,460 --> 01:13:20,479
[SPEAKER_00] naš brat iz Franjačkog svjetovnog reda,

782
01:13:20,479 --> 01:13:23,199
[SPEAKER_00] koji evo koordinira

783
01:13:23,199 --> 01:13:24,859
[SPEAKER_00] i vodi brigu baš

784
01:13:24,859 --> 01:13:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] o kompletnom razvoju

785
01:13:26,939 --> 01:13:28,359
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga projekta.

786
01:13:29,420 --> 01:13:30,859
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala da je on tu,

787
01:13:30,859 --> 01:13:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] da nije njega bilo to,

788
01:13:32,039 --> 01:13:32,560
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

789
01:13:32,560 --> 01:13:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] mi bi još uvijek ostali na mailu,

790
01:13:34,300 --> 01:13:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] dobri stari mail,

791
01:13:36,159 --> 01:13:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] tako da Vlado je tu povezan

792
01:13:39,239 --> 01:13:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] sa drugim programerima

793
01:13:41,380 --> 01:13:42,560
[SPEAKER_00] koji su tu uključeni,

794
01:13:42,560 --> 01:13:43,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

795
01:13:43,180 --> 01:13:44,500
[SPEAKER_00] smijeli spominjati,

796
01:13:44,500 --> 01:13:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] bojim se da ću se pobrgati,

797
01:13:45,640 --> 01:13:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] Petar Čurković,

798
01:13:46,840 --> 01:13:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] Daniel Vincijanović,

799
01:13:48,579 --> 01:13:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] evo to su nam tri programera

800
01:13:50,000 --> 01:13:51,819
[SPEAKER_00] koji su ono baš stalno tu

801
01:13:51,819 --> 01:13:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] i od srca,

802
01:13:52,640 --> 01:13:53,600
[SPEAKER_00] od srca im hvala.

803
01:13:53,600 --> 01:13:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zatim neizostavni naši lektori,

804
01:13:55,880 --> 01:13:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] evo oni se trude da naši tekstovi

805
01:13:58,180 --> 01:13:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi pišemo

806
01:13:58,819 --> 01:14:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] budu jezično dotjerani,

807
01:14:01,039 --> 01:14:03,600
[SPEAKER_00] evo oni popravljaju ono što mi zbrljamo.

808
01:14:03,600 --> 01:14:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] To je naša draga Marija Štanco

809
01:14:05,819 --> 01:14:08,140
[SPEAKER_00] i Miroslav Pavlić.

810
01:14:08,140 --> 01:14:10,060
[SPEAKER_00] Evo dakle oni u svoj slobodno vrijeme,

811
01:14:10,060 --> 01:14:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] volonterski kao i svi drugi,

812
01:14:11,859 --> 01:14:14,060
[SPEAKER_00] pomažu sređuju tekstove

813
01:14:14,060 --> 01:14:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] i tu je odnedavno jedna ekipa

814
01:14:17,300 --> 01:14:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] koja snima,

815
01:14:18,640 --> 01:14:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] jer sad imamo i audio verziju,

816
01:14:20,300 --> 01:14:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] ne uvijek,

817
01:14:20,899 --> 01:14:22,380
