818
01:14:22,380 --> 01:14:25,840
[SPEAKER_00] Isto moram paziti da dobro to sve spomenem,

819
01:14:25,840 --> 01:14:27,100
[SPEAKER_00] to je Dijana Tikvić,

820
01:14:27,100 --> 01:14:30,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ana Marija Buntić,

821
01:14:30,260 --> 01:14:32,319
[SPEAKER_00] Loretta Rabar,

822
01:14:32,319 --> 01:14:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] Branimir Gubić,

823
01:14:35,539 --> 01:14:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] Jozo Lukić

824
01:14:39,119 --> 01:14:42,720
[SPEAKER_00] i Mihael Vrbanić.

825
01:14:42,720 --> 01:14:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislila sam sve

826
01:14:43,659 --> 01:14:46,399
[SPEAKER_00] i da nisam nekome zaboravio prezime.

827
01:14:46,399 --> 01:14:50,000
[SPEAKER_00] I evo još samo neću više gnjavit sa imenima,

828
01:14:50,000 --> 01:14:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] tu su naši ovaj

829
01:14:51,420 --> 01:14:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] Monteri ili Ton Majstori,

830
01:14:54,699 --> 01:14:56,439
[SPEAKER_00] to je naš Luka Rupčić

831
01:14:56,439 --> 01:14:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] i spomenuti Mihael koji također pomaže

832
01:14:58,680 --> 01:14:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao Ton Majstori.

833
01:14:59,739 --> 01:15:00,739
[SPEAKER_01] Evo možemo navesti

834
01:15:00,739 --> 01:15:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] suradnik u pisanju Efe Riječi,

835
01:15:03,460 --> 01:15:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] tu je i naš Fran Nikola Juršić,

836
01:15:05,079 --> 01:15:05,979
[SPEAKER_01] naš prvi gost,

837
01:15:05,979 --> 01:15:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi su na komentarima pisali

838
01:15:07,960 --> 01:15:08,859
[SPEAKER_01] kako uživaju

839
