840
01:15:11,739 --> 01:15:13,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je naš pjesnik,

841
01:15:13,659 --> 01:15:15,020
[SPEAKER_00] Nikola je naš pjesnik

842
01:15:15,020 --> 01:15:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] u Efe Riječi.

843
01:15:16,159 --> 01:15:17,640
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je Fran Marko,

844
01:15:17,640 --> 01:15:18,979
[SPEAKER_00] tu je Stjepan Lice,

845
01:15:18,979 --> 01:15:20,539
[SPEAKER_00] Fraželjko Barbarić,

846
01:15:20,539 --> 01:15:21,859
[SPEAKER_00] sestra Sunčica,

847
01:15:21,859 --> 01:15:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kunić,

848
01:15:22,739 --> 01:15:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] Fradarko Tepert,

849
01:15:24,159 --> 01:15:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] Marinko Ia,

850
01:15:25,239 --> 01:15:26,779
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam.

851
01:15:27,020 --> 01:15:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] To je manje više taj kvijep.

852
01:15:28,279 --> 01:15:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je to.

853
01:15:28,380 --> 01:15:30,500
[SPEAKER_01] I ti si me naiva sjećan.

854
01:15:30,500 --> 01:15:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

