1035
01:20:25,260 --> 01:20:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] o vjernosti Franjevačkoj karizmi.

1036
01:20:27,739 --> 01:20:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo garant,

1037
01:20:28,680 --> 01:20:29,840
[SPEAKER_00] recimo tako,

1038
01:20:29,840 --> 01:20:31,239
[SPEAKER_00] jedan da, evo,

1039
01:20:31,239 --> 01:20:33,140
[SPEAKER_00] svjetovni Franjevci,

1040
01:20:33,140 --> 01:20:34,520
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno bratstva na

1041
01:20:34,520 --> 01:20:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] mjesnoj, područnoj,

1042
01:20:36,039 --> 01:20:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] nacionalnoj i međunarodnoj razini,

1043
01:20:37,840 --> 01:20:39,300
[SPEAKER_00] da žive, evo,

1044
01:20:39,300 --> 01:20:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] da su vjerni

1045
01:20:40,380 --> 01:20:41,560
[SPEAKER_00] toj Franjevačkoj karizmi.

1046
01:20:41,560 --> 01:20:44,439
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to je nekako ono

1047
