1062
01:21:09,420 --> 01:21:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih u ovom trenutku

1063
01:21:11,239 --> 01:21:13,039
[SPEAKER_00] odao jedno veliko priznanje

1064
01:21:13,039 --> 01:21:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] tim našim ženama

1065
01:21:15,399 --> 01:21:16,359
[SPEAKER_00] bakicama,

1066
01:21:16,359 --> 01:21:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] trećaricama,

1067
01:21:17,300 --> 01:21:18,779
[SPEAKER_00] koje su, evo,

1068
01:21:18,779 --> 01:21:20,779
[SPEAKER_00] kroz to teško vrijeme komunizma

1069
01:21:20,779 --> 01:21:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] baš onako

1070
01:21:22,960 --> 01:21:24,420
[SPEAKER_00] ostale vjerne

1071
01:21:24,420 --> 01:21:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] i čuvale su

1072
01:21:26,000 --> 01:21:27,560
[SPEAKER_00] da trećeg reda

1073
01:21:27,560 --> 01:21:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] ne nestane.

1074
01:21:28,520 --> 01:21:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] to su bile pobožne žene,

1075
01:21:30,140 --> 01:21:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] žene koje su ljubile Boga,

1076
01:21:31,800 --> 01:21:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje su ljubile svoju crkvu,

1077
01:21:33,420 --> 01:21:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] koje su bile podrška svojim fratrima,

1078
01:21:36,340 --> 01:21:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek su bili tu i

1079
01:21:37,680 --> 01:21:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] to su žene koje su

1080
01:21:39,920 --> 01:21:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] bile pojam čestitosti

1081
01:21:42,600 --> 01:21:44,560
[SPEAKER_00] u svojim mjestima.

1082
01:21:44,560 --> 01:21:47,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sad mi pada na pamet jedna simpatična stvar,

1083
01:21:47,899 --> 01:21:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ja bio dijete

1084
01:21:48,960 --> 01:21:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] i to je se spominjalo

1085
01:21:51,239 --> 01:21:52,859
[SPEAKER_00] sultara trećarice,

1086
01:21:52,859 --> 01:21:54,060
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja sam mislio

1087
01:21:54,060 --> 01:21:55,180
[SPEAKER_00] su to žene koje sjede

1088
01:21:55,180 --> 01:21:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] u trećem redu u crkvu.

1089
01:21:57,420 --> 01:22:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] A stvarno te neke bake

1090
01:22:00,800 --> 01:22:02,560
[SPEAKER_00] iz moga sela su bile trećarice,

1091
01:22:02,560 --> 01:22:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] nosili su ovaj pasić

1092
01:22:04,039 --> 01:22:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] ili o svojoj suknji

1093
01:22:05,140 --> 01:22:06,439
[SPEAKER_00] i sjedili su u trećem redu.

1094
01:22:06,439 --> 01:22:08,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam to tako nekako povezal.

1095
01:22:08,060 --> 01:22:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno,

1096
01:22:08,579 --> 01:22:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] da mi je to kasnije bilo smiješno.

1097
01:22:10,579 --> 01:22:12,060
[SPEAKER_01] Da je ovaj.

1098
01:22:12,060 --> 01:22:14,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo kako privući mlade

1099
01:22:14,180 --> 01:22:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] u treći red.

1100
01:22:14,960 --> 01:22:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] Evo vi ste radili s mladima,

1101
01:22:16,380 --> 01:22:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] bilo ste duhovni asident frame.

1102
01:22:18,079 --> 01:22:20,399
[SPEAKER_01] Mladima ostane nekako često

1103
01:22:20,399 --> 01:22:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] ta predrasuda da su tu stariji,

1104
01:22:22,420 --> 01:22:24,359
[SPEAKER_01] da to još nije za njih.

1105
01:22:24,359 --> 01:22:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] Možda ne da nije nikako za njih,

1106
01:22:27,199 --> 01:22:28,140
[SPEAKER_01] nego da nije još.

1107
01:22:28,140 --> 01:22:29,979
[SPEAKER_01] Evo i ja sam osobno imao

1108
01:22:29,979 --> 01:22:31,220
[SPEAKER_01] tu neku predrasudu,

1109
01:22:31,220 --> 01:22:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali opet poziv je poziv,

1110
01:22:33,539 --> 01:22:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] nebitno tko se nalazi u redu.

1111
01:22:36,800 --> 01:22:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Točno to.

1112
01:22:38,659 --> 01:22:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevački svjetovni red je,

1113
01:22:41,300 --> 01:22:43,819
[SPEAKER_00] nije to jedna molitvena zajednica.

1114
01:22:43,819 --> 01:22:47,439
[SPEAKER_00] Pripadnost Franjevačkom svjetovnom redu

1115
01:22:47,439 --> 01:22:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] je na duge staze.

1116
01:22:49,739 --> 01:22:51,020
[SPEAKER_00] u Franjevačkom svjetovnom redu

1117
01:22:51,020 --> 01:22:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] nakon formacije,

1118
01:22:52,239 --> 01:22:54,100
[SPEAKER_00] znači nakon simpatizerstva,

1119
01:22:54,100 --> 01:22:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] nakon novicijata,

1120
01:22:55,239 --> 01:22:57,479
[SPEAKER_00] koje negdje traje i do dvije godine

1121
01:22:57,479 --> 01:22:58,979
[SPEAKER_00] nakon priveremenih zavijeta,

1122
01:22:58,979 --> 01:23:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] daju se doživotnih zavijeti,

1123
01:23:00,920 --> 01:23:01,939
[SPEAKER_00] trajnih zavijeti.

1124
01:23:01,939 --> 01:23:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako se osoba trajno obvezuje

1125
01:23:04,840 --> 01:23:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] da će živjeti u bratstvu.

1126
01:23:06,220 --> 01:23:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] I možda je to ono što ljude plaši.

1127
01:23:10,739 --> 01:23:14,479
[SPEAKER_00] kao ono ne želim se trajno vezati

1128
01:23:14,479 --> 01:23:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] ni za koga.

1129
01:23:15,899 --> 01:23:20,800
[SPEAKER_00] Također u Franjevačkom svjetovnom redu,

1130
01:23:20,800 --> 01:23:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] to može i ti možeš reći,

1131
01:23:22,239 --> 01:23:24,020
[SPEAKER_00] nema ništa spektakularno.

1132
01:23:24,020 --> 01:23:26,899
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna duboka duhovnost,

1133
01:23:26,899 --> 01:23:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] ali jedna jako jednostavna duhovnost.

1134
01:23:29,659 --> 01:23:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] Obveze svjetovnih Franjevaca je,

1135
01:23:32,800 --> 01:23:34,500
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče molitve,

1136
01:23:34,500 --> 01:23:35,899
[SPEAKER_00] molitva časoslova

1137
01:23:35,899 --> 01:23:39,579
[SPEAKER_00] i život u bratstvu.

1138
01:23:39,579 --> 01:23:42,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ja mislim da to za mladog čovjeka,

1139
01:23:42,500 --> 01:23:44,060
[SPEAKER_00] ne ipak premladoga,

1140
01:23:44,060 --> 01:23:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovisno kako čovjek nekako to osjeti,

1141
01:23:45,960 --> 01:23:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] da to može biti jedna lijepa struktura.

1142
01:23:48,420 --> 01:23:50,340
[SPEAKER_00] Rekli smo da je to red,

1143
01:23:50,340 --> 01:23:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] da svoje sjedište ima u Rimu,

1144
01:23:52,720 --> 01:23:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] da o tom redu brine

1145
01:23:55,880 --> 01:23:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] sveta stolica,

1146
01:23:57,119 --> 01:23:58,800
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dala i pravilo,

1147
01:23:58,800 --> 01:24:00,520
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dala generalne konstitucije.

1148
01:24:00,520 --> 01:24:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da je to jedan siguran put.

1149
01:24:03,720 --> 01:24:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] To nije nikako eksperimentiranje,

1150
01:24:05,720 --> 01:24:07,020
[SPEAKER_00] nego jedan provjeren put,

1151
01:24:07,020 --> 01:24:09,060
[SPEAKER_00] put koji je star 800 godina.

1152
01:24:09,060 --> 01:24:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] I ako neko bi htio,

1153
01:24:10,960 --> 01:24:11,640
[SPEAKER_00] recimo tako,

1154
01:24:11,640 --> 01:24:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] živjeti svoje kršćanstvo

1155
01:24:13,260 --> 01:24:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] i naći neku zajednicu

1156
01:24:15,380 --> 01:24:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] koja će mu pomoći

1157
01:24:16,399 --> 01:24:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] da to kršćanstvo nekako

1158
01:24:18,500 --> 01:24:21,359
[SPEAKER_00] procvjeta njegovo kršćanstvo

1159
01:24:21,359 --> 01:24:22,340
[SPEAKER_00] ili njegova krsna milost

1160
01:24:22,340 --> 01:24:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] da procvjeta,

1161
01:24:22,920 --> 01:24:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] da donese nekakve plodove,

1162
01:24:24,760 --> 01:24:25,600
[SPEAKER_00] ja vjerujem da mu

1163
01:24:25,600 --> 01:24:26,939
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevčki svjetovni red

1164
01:24:26,939 --> 01:24:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] i sveti Franju

1165
01:24:28,039 --> 01:24:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] mogu tu biti jedna

1166
01:24:29,000 --> 01:24:30,720
[SPEAKER_00] lijepa prigoda.

1167
01:24:30,720 --> 01:24:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, ne bi se smijela

1168
01:24:32,920 --> 01:24:33,619
[SPEAKER_00] odluka donositi

1169
01:24:33,619 --> 01:24:34,380
[SPEAKER_00] ili tamo, ne znam,

1170
01:24:34,380 --> 01:24:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] nije deset bakica

1171
01:24:35,539 --> 01:24:36,640
[SPEAKER_00] ili je tamo,

1172
01:24:36,640 --> 01:24:37,020
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1173
01:24:37,020 --> 01:24:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] nija mlađa ekipa.

1174
01:24:38,319 --> 01:24:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] To može biti isto

1175
01:24:39,500 --> 01:24:40,840
[SPEAKER_00] nešto što je,

1176
01:24:40,840 --> 01:24:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] recimo tako,

1177
01:24:41,659 --> 01:24:42,560
[SPEAKER_00] lakšavajuća

1178
01:24:42,560 --> 01:24:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] ili otežavajuća okolnost,

1179
01:24:43,859 --> 01:24:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali stvar je

1180
01:24:44,920 --> 01:24:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] negdje drugo,

1181
01:24:45,840 --> 01:24:46,220
[SPEAKER_00] ono...

1182
01:24:46,220 --> 01:24:47,060
[SPEAKER_00] To je predpoziv.

1183
01:24:47,060 --> 01:24:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako.

1184
01:24:47,720 --> 01:24:48,159
[SPEAKER_00] Poslani poziv.

1185
01:24:48,159 --> 01:24:49,060
[SPEAKER_00] Tako, upravo to je.

1186
01:24:49,220 --> 01:24:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] možda poziv koji su mi nekako osjetili

1187
01:24:51,159 --> 01:24:52,899
[SPEAKER_01] na Franju kroz svoje framaštvo,

1188
01:24:52,899 --> 01:24:56,560
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je son možda tek ono aktualizirat,

1189
01:24:56,560 --> 01:24:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] tako tako, mogu reći realizirat u trećem red.

1190
01:24:59,619 --> 01:25:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sjećam, to je malo mene živcirala,

1191
01:25:02,260 --> 01:25:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] ta izjava gdje jedna i bivša framašica i trećarica

1192
01:25:05,659 --> 01:25:06,539
[SPEAKER_01] spominjala,

1193
01:25:07,359 --> 01:25:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ste vi framaši u trećem red,

1194
01:25:10,239 --> 01:25:11,399
[SPEAKER_01] kako vas nema.

1195
01:25:11,399 --> 01:25:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] Kao postavlja se pitanje,

1196
01:25:13,220 --> 01:25:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] jeste li kad bili framaši,

1197
01:25:14,840 --> 01:25:17,560
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne nastavljate dalje u trećem red.

1198
01:25:17,560 --> 01:25:19,140
[SPEAKER_01] To je mene nekako živciralo,

1199
01:25:19,140 --> 01:25:22,180
[SPEAKER_01] ono, kako možeš nekako tako govoriti,

1200
01:25:22,180 --> 01:25:23,479
[SPEAKER_01] ali ubiti kasnije, ono,

1201
01:25:23,479 --> 01:25:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] i shvatio sam o čemu se tu radi,

1202
01:25:26,340 --> 01:25:28,180
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

1203
01:25:28,180 --> 01:25:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] nekako bi tu razlučio,

1204
01:25:30,239 --> 01:25:32,140
[SPEAKER_01] malo je ružno reći,

1205
01:25:32,140 --> 01:25:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] ono, kakav si framaš, ono,

1206
01:25:34,539 --> 01:25:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] ako ne ideš u trećem red,

1207
01:25:36,539 --> 01:25:38,560
[SPEAKER_01] možda je bolje razlučio to malo,

1208
01:25:38,560 --> 01:25:40,899
[SPEAKER_01] na članove frame nekako i framaše,

1209
01:25:40,899 --> 01:25:41,899
[SPEAKER_01] koji su, evo, rećemo,

1210
01:25:41,899 --> 01:25:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] baš framaši puno u smislu riječ,

1211
01:25:44,579 --> 01:25:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] koji su stvarno ostali i zadržali taj svoj poziv,

1212
01:25:47,800 --> 01:25:51,140
[SPEAKER_01] jer evo i kroz fratr uđu i izađu neki,

1213
01:25:51,140 --> 01:25:53,640
[SPEAKER_01] tako i kroz framu prođu,

1214
01:25:53,640 --> 01:25:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] i možda nisu baš bili tu s tim pravim pozivom,

1215
01:25:59,420 --> 01:26:00,779
[SPEAKER_01] kao i za fratre,

1216
01:26:00,779 --> 01:26:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] i tek onda kasnije možda razlučiš

1217
01:26:03,739 --> 01:26:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] što je tvoj poziv i priključiš se.

1218
01:26:06,760 --> 01:26:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] Imam ideju jednu,

1219
01:26:08,100 --> 01:26:10,979
[SPEAKER_00] ja predlažem da nekad, recimo, za dvije godine,

1220
01:26:10,979 --> 01:26:12,779
[SPEAKER_00] ja budem tu na tvojom mjestu,

1221
01:26:12,779 --> 01:26:14,680
[SPEAKER_00] a ti je da udeš ovdje,

1222
01:26:14,680 --> 01:26:17,560
[SPEAKER_00] da ja tebe ispitujem u Franjačkom svjetovnom redu

1223
01:26:17,560 --> 01:26:18,979
[SPEAKER_00] i da vodimo dijalog o...

1224
01:26:18,979 --> 01:26:20,920
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš, dogovorit ćemo se.

1225
01:26:20,920 --> 01:26:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, ajde.

1226
01:26:21,460 --> 01:26:23,800
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo sad snimljeno, pa evo,

1227
01:26:23,800 --> 01:26:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] vi podsjetite,

1228
01:26:25,319 --> 01:26:28,460
[SPEAKER_01] imamo gledatelji su ovaj svjedoci,

1229
01:26:28,460 --> 01:26:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] dogovore tako da...

1230
01:26:29,180 --> 01:26:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] To be continued ove tebe.

1231
01:26:30,840 --> 01:26:31,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, evo,

1232
01:26:31,579 --> 01:26:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo, možda kako još malo aktualizirati

1233
01:26:35,340 --> 01:26:37,279
[SPEAKER_01] među mladima treći red,

1234
01:26:37,279 --> 01:26:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] možda da više ih ohrabri,

1235
01:26:39,399 --> 01:26:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne boje pristupiti,

1236
01:26:40,840 --> 01:26:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] može isključiti neke predrasude,

1237
01:26:43,979 --> 01:26:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, treći red bi trebao skrbići za Frama,

1238
01:26:46,920 --> 01:26:49,520
[SPEAKER_01] jer je Frama ogranak trećeg reda.

1239
01:26:49,520 --> 01:26:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, Frama postoji,

1240
01:26:51,720 --> 01:26:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] kao evo, zajednica mladi,

1241
01:26:53,460 --> 01:26:55,920
[SPEAKER_00] ona živi u okrilju

1242
01:26:55,920 --> 01:26:57,939
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevačkog svjetovnog reda.

1243
01:26:57,939 --> 01:27:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne bi tu ništa forsirao.

1244
01:27:00,800 --> 01:27:02,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je jako važno

1245
01:27:02,439 --> 01:27:04,279
[SPEAKER_00] da mi Franjevci,

1246
01:27:04,279 --> 01:27:07,439
[SPEAKER_00] ja, ti, sestre Klarise,

1247
01:27:07,439 --> 01:27:08,579
[SPEAKER_00] sestre Franjevke,

1248
01:27:08,579 --> 01:27:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] ali također,

1249
01:27:09,300 --> 01:27:12,579
[SPEAKER_00] koje su dio Franjevačkog

1250
01:27:12,579 --> 01:27:14,399
[SPEAKER_00] trećeg samostanskog reda.

1251
01:27:14,399 --> 01:27:16,020
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da mi samo trebamo

1252
01:27:16,020 --> 01:27:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] biti autentični.

1253
01:27:16,760 --> 01:27:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da mi samo trebamo biti ono,

1254
01:27:19,300 --> 01:27:22,600
[SPEAKER_00] dobri sinovi svetog Franje,

1255
01:27:22,600 --> 01:27:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] sinovi kćeri svetog Franje,

1256
01:27:24,039 --> 01:27:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] ko će nam se pridružiti,

1257
01:27:27,260 --> 01:27:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] kad će nam se pridružiti,

1258
01:27:28,859 --> 01:27:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] evanđelje ne poznaje lobiranje.

1259
01:27:32,420 --> 01:27:33,520
[SPEAKER_01] Da, mislim,

1260
01:27:33,520 --> 01:27:34,659
[SPEAKER_01] i Franjevnikoga nije znao.

1261
01:27:34,659 --> 01:27:36,100
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako, evo.

1262
01:27:36,100 --> 01:27:38,180
[SPEAKER_00] Svojim životom je privukao.

1263
01:27:38,180 --> 01:27:39,939
[SPEAKER_00] Mi trebamo navještati Krista,

1264
01:27:41,000 --> 01:27:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] nasljedovati Krista,

1265
01:27:42,199 --> 01:27:43,319
[SPEAKER_00] živjeti s Kristom,

1266
01:27:43,319 --> 01:27:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] biti dobri,

1267
01:27:44,760 --> 01:27:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] biti Boži,

1268
01:27:45,699 --> 01:27:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] biti braća i sestre jedni drugima.

1269
