[SPEAKER_00] ono je to sasvim jasno,

1487
01:32:16,359 --> 01:32:18,180
[SPEAKER_00] ja znam gdje je moje mjesto

1488
01:32:18,180 --> 01:32:19,979
[SPEAKER_00] i Bog će me na kraju pitati,

1489
01:32:19,979 --> 01:32:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] jeli?

1490
01:32:20,199 --> 01:32:22,140
[SPEAKER_00] Moja zadaća je

1491
01:32:22,140 --> 01:32:23,220
[SPEAKER_00] biti u bratstvu

1492
01:32:23,220 --> 01:32:24,199
[SPEAKER_00] i moja zadaća,

1493
01:32:24,199 --> 01:32:25,020
[SPEAKER_00] moj poziv,

1494
01:32:25,180 --> 01:32:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam ja to slobodno prihvatio

1495
01:32:26,800 --> 01:32:28,159
[SPEAKER_00] i kada sam to slobodno prihvatio,

1496
01:32:28,159 --> 01:32:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] to postaje moj poziv i obveza,

1497
01:32:29,720 --> 01:32:31,439
[SPEAKER_00] a moja zadaća je čuvati

1498
01:32:31,439 --> 01:32:33,520
[SPEAKER_00] u svijetu i u crkvi

1499
01:32:33,520 --> 01:32:34,479
[SPEAKER_00] Franjevačku karizmu.

1500
01:32:34,479 --> 01:32:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ne biti karizmatik,

1501
01:32:37,239 --> 01:32:38,680
[SPEAKER_00] jeli?

1502
01:32:38,680 --> 01:32:41,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ima osoba koja ima poziv

1503
01:32:41,680 --> 01:32:42,520
[SPEAKER_00] i biti karizmatik

1504
01:32:42,520 --> 01:32:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] i ona treba to biti

1505
01:32:44,460 --> 01:32:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] u skladu sa svojim putem,

1506
01:32:46,079 --> 01:32:47,100
[SPEAKER_00] putem svoje zajednice

1507
01:32:47,100 --> 01:32:48,100
[SPEAKER_00] i ona će pred Bogom

1508
01:32:48,100 --> 01:32:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] za to odgovarati.

1509
01:32:49,000 --> 01:32:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] A Franjevač,

1510
01:32:50,220 --> 01:32:51,119
[SPEAKER_00] svjetovni Franjevač

1511
01:32:51,119 --> 01:32:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] zna se gdje moje mjesto je.

1512
01:32:52,380 --> 01:32:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo, danas

1513
01:32:54,159 --> 01:32:55,939
[SPEAKER_01] možda i među trećarima

1514
01:32:55,939 --> 01:32:57,699
[SPEAKER_01] nekim popularno

1515
01:32:57,699 --> 01:32:59,140
[SPEAKER_01] da se i oni traže

1516
01:32:59,140 --> 01:33:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] u tim karizmatskim vodama,

1517
01:33:01,300 --> 01:33:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali nekako gledam na to

1518
01:33:04,260 --> 01:33:05,979
[SPEAKER_01] da je to možda iz razloga

1519
01:33:05,979 --> 01:33:07,279
[SPEAKER_01] što nisu dovoljno upoznali

1520
01:33:07,279 --> 01:33:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] Franjevačku karizmu

1521
01:33:08,319 --> 01:33:10,720
[SPEAKER_01] i tko je u istinu svjeti Franjevač.

1522
01:33:10,779 --> 01:33:13,060
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro, čovjek se ima pravo

1523
01:33:13,060 --> 01:33:13,859
[SPEAKER_00] tražiti, jel?

1524
01:33:13,859 --> 01:33:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] To je samo ne,

1525
01:33:14,699 --> 01:33:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] to traženje mora prestati, jel?

1526
01:33:16,920 --> 01:33:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može cijeli život biti

1527
01:33:17,880 --> 01:33:19,859
[SPEAKER_00] traženje i šaranje, jel?

1528
01:33:19,859 --> 01:33:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] Negdje se treba opredijeliti, jel?

1529
01:33:21,800 --> 01:33:24,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ok, ljudi, ljudi, jel?

1530
01:33:24,319 --> 01:33:25,800
[SPEAKER_00] Možda u nekom trenutku

1531
01:33:25,800 --> 01:33:26,979
[SPEAKER_00] svog života imaju potrebu

1532
01:33:26,979 --> 01:33:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] tako preispitivati,

1533
01:33:28,819 --> 01:33:29,560
[SPEAKER_00] tražiti.

1534
01:33:29,560 --> 01:33:32,239
[SPEAKER_01] Franjevačku,

1535
01:33:32,239 --> 01:33:32,960
[SPEAKER_01] evo mi smo se

1536
01:33:32,960 --> 01:33:34,840
[SPEAKER_01] raspričali i napričali

1537
01:33:34,840 --> 01:33:35,520
[SPEAKER_01] prilično,

1538
01:33:35,520 --> 01:33:37,659
[SPEAKER_01] dobro standardno

1539
01:33:37,659 --> 01:33:38,600
[SPEAKER_01] naših sati.

1540
01:33:38,600 --> 01:33:40,140
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, fraj Espe,

1541
01:33:40,140 --> 01:33:42,260
[SPEAKER_01] hoćete li neku završnu poruku

1542
01:33:42,260 --> 01:33:43,739
[SPEAKER_01] reći našim gledateljima,

1543
01:33:43,739 --> 01:33:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] nešto u vezi molitve

1544
01:33:45,039 --> 01:33:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili općenito, nešto?

1545
01:33:46,159 --> 01:33:50,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je Ivan Pavao drugi

1546
01:33:50,960 --> 01:33:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] jednom rekao

1547
01:33:52,539 --> 01:33:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] moli kako god znaš,

1548
01:33:54,239 --> 01:33:55,939
[SPEAKER_00] samo, samo moli.

1549
01:33:55,939 --> 01:33:59,399
[SPEAKER_00] A ja bi tu malo nekako dodao

1550
01:33:59,399 --> 01:34:01,060
[SPEAKER_00] čezni za Bogom.

1551
01:34:01,060 --> 01:34:03,100
[SPEAKER_00] Čezni za Bogom.

1552
01:34:03,680 --> 01:34:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] ljubi Boga.

1553
01:34:04,340 --> 01:34:06,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ako čezneš za Bogom,

1554
01:34:06,779 --> 01:34:10,439
[SPEAKER_00] onda će biti moguće

1555
01:34:10,439 --> 01:34:11,939
[SPEAKER_00] reći to

1556
01:34:11,939 --> 01:34:12,979
[SPEAKER_00] moli kako god.

1557
01:34:12,979 --> 01:34:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako se moja molitva

1558
01:34:14,920 --> 01:34:16,399
[SPEAKER_00] bilo usmena,

1559
01:34:16,399 --> 01:34:17,640
[SPEAKER_00] bilo misaona,

1560
01:34:17,640 --> 01:34:19,220
[SPEAKER_00] bilo molitva šutnja,

1561
01:34:19,220 --> 01:34:20,819
[SPEAKER_00] ako se ona rađa iščežnje

1562
01:34:20,819 --> 01:34:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] za Bogom,

1563
01:34:22,239 --> 01:34:24,520
[SPEAKER_00] ona mora biti dobra.

1564
01:34:24,520 --> 01:34:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što bi ja ponovim.

1565
01:34:28,239 --> 01:34:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] Molite,

1566
01:34:28,819 --> 01:34:31,199
[SPEAKER_00] čeznući

1567
01:34:31,199 --> 01:34:33,199
[SPEAKER_00] i čeznite moleći.

1568
01:34:33,680 --> 01:34:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam što ste izvojili vrijeme,

1569
01:34:37,000 --> 01:34:38,880
[SPEAKER_01] što ste došli nama u goste.

1570
01:34:38,880 --> 01:34:41,640
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ćemo se po dogovoru opet.

1571
01:34:41,640 --> 01:34:44,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ne prije, za dvije godine.

1572
01:34:44,020 --> 01:34:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, hvala.

1573
01:34:46,579 --> 01:34:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je prvi put da sam ja u tom podcastu.

1574
01:34:48,779 --> 01:34:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] U trenutku mi je bilo vruće,

1575
01:34:52,000 --> 01:34:54,319
[SPEAKER_00] ali skušao sam da je to od nekakve treme,

1576
01:34:54,859 --> 01:34:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] i pusti refraktora

1577
01:34:56,100 --> 01:34:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo mi je na kraju ugodno.

1578
01:34:57,539 --> 01:34:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, razbili smo raket.

1579
01:34:58,739 --> 01:35:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo mi je lijepo,

1580
01:35:00,119 --> 01:35:01,699
[SPEAKER_00] bilo mi je lijepo i evo, hvala.

1581
01:35:01,699 --> 01:35:03,659
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala i radite dobru stvar.

1582
01:35:03,659 --> 01:35:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] Radite dobru stvar samo naprijed.

1583
01:35:05,420 --> 01:35:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam.

1584
01:35:06,880 --> 01:35:08,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi naši gledatelji,

1585
01:35:08,199 --> 01:35:11,560
[SPEAKER_01] evo, došli smo do kraja nove još jedne epizode.

1586
01:35:11,560 --> 01:35:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] Sve vas pozivam da nas zapratite,

1587
01:35:14,380 --> 01:35:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] da lajkajte video ako vam se svidio,

1588
01:35:16,340 --> 01:35:17,140
[SPEAKER_01] da podijelite,

1589
01:35:17,140 --> 01:35:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] da do drugih.

1590
01:35:18,500 --> 01:35:18,939
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

1591
01:35:18,939 --> 01:35:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] nama ti lajkovi nešto posebno,

1592
01:35:21,880 --> 01:35:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] osobno i ne znače,

1593
01:35:23,920 --> 01:35:24,279
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo,

1594
01:35:24,279 --> 01:35:26,880
[SPEAKER_01] zbog algoritma i tih stvari,

1595
01:35:26,880 --> 01:35:29,819
[SPEAKER_01] načina funkcioniranja YouTube-a,

1596
01:35:30,159 --> 01:35:31,899
[SPEAKER_01] pozivamo vas da lajkate,

1597
01:35:31,899 --> 01:35:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] da do što većeg broja ljudi

1598
01:35:34,159 --> 01:35:35,699
[SPEAKER_01] dopre ova epizoda,

1599
01:35:35,699 --> 01:35:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] ova naša poruka,

1600
01:35:36,619 --> 01:35:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] naš rad.

1601
01:35:37,340 --> 01:35:40,279
[SPEAKER_01] Zapratite nas i na našim društvenim mrežama,

1602
01:35:40,279 --> 01:35:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] na Instagramu i Facebooku.

1603
01:35:42,239 --> 01:35:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] A evo,

1604
01:35:42,760 --> 01:35:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] do sljedećeg osa,

1605
01:35:44,199 --> 01:35:45,460
[SPEAKER_01] do sljedećeg epizode.

1606
01:35:45,460 --> 01:35:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] Mir vam i dobro.

